{"tid":1697001,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞和街糧食店被罰暫停營業十四天","createTime":"2019-11-06T14:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T09:43:12.000Z","uid":7439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"494c0c93adebebddd4cc44cf5e31c3d5139a5413","tid":1697001,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:23:19.000Z","msg":"觀塘新鮮糧食店被罰暫停營業十四天<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  觀塘一新鮮糧食店經營者因非法擴展營業範圍，屢次違反《食物業規例》，被食物環境衞生署（食環署）署長暫時吊銷牌照十四天。<br />\n   <br />\n  店鋪名為「興聯」，位於觀塘瑞和街26號地下，須由今日（十一月六日）至十一月十九日暫停營業。<br />\n   <br />\n  食環署發言人說：「有關店鋪經營者因上述違例事項，今年二月及三月兩次被法庭定罪，共罰款一萬零五百元。本署亦根據違例記分制記下持牌人三十分，店鋪因此須停牌十四天。」<br />\n   <br />\n  有關持牌人亦因相同違例事項，去年九月及今年二月兩次被法庭定罪，共罰款七千九百元，因而被記下三十分，店鋪今年五月被暫時吊銷牌照七天。<br />\n   <br />\n  發言人提醒食物業處所持牌人必須遵守《食物業規例》，否則牌照可能被暫時吊銷或取消。<br />\n   <br />\n  持牌食物業處所須在處所入口附近顯眼處展示已領有牌照的告示，以資識別。此外，市民亦可瀏覽食環署網頁（<a href=\"http://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/licensing/index.html）查閱持牌食物業處所名單。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Flicensing%2Findex.html%EF%BC%89%E6%9F%A5%E9%96%B1%E6%8C%81%E7%89%8C%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD%E8%99%95%E6%89%80%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E3%80%82&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNa3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=18f1db07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/licensing/index.html）查閱持牌食物業處所名單。</a><br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年11月6日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間15時00分"},{"pid":"88d698c8aba7410cc2cbeddd6203680544529ab5","tid":1697001,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/licensing/list_premises_suspended.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Flicensing%2Flist_premises_suspended.html&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNa3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=48d49e02\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_chi/licensing/list_premises_suspended.html</a><br />\n觀塘 新鮮糧食店 九龍觀塘 瑞和街26號地下 興聯 06-11-2019 -<br />\n19-11-2019<br />\n(14 天)<br />\n<br />\n觀塘 新鮮糧食店 九龍觀塘 瑞和街26號地下 興聯 24-05-2019 -<br />\n30-05-2019<br />\n(7 天)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢間唔係第一次 <br />\n好多瑞和街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc504107c4cde2aee0046cd7fa4197e8f965861b","tid":1697001,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b3/HK_Kwun_Tong_evening_%E7%91%9E%E5%92%8C%E8%A1%97_Shui_Wo_Street_market_%E8%88%88%E8%81%AF%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98_Brilliant_Charm_Supermarket_food_group_visitors.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fb%2Fb3%2FHK_Kwun_Tong_evening_%25E7%2591%259E%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25A1%2597_Shui_Wo_Street_market_%25E8%2588%2588%25E8%2581%25AF%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%259C%2598_Brilliant_Charm_Supermarket_food_group_visitors.JPG&h=970207b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20190906/photo/bkn-20190906190017129-0906_00982_001_01p.jpg?20190906190400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190906%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190906190017129-0906_00982_001_01p.jpg%3F20190906190400&h=7bd3472a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車然係咁：障礙處處的瑞和街<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560631</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條街對於觀塘區街坊而言無人不識，因為長期被兩旁商舖放滿雜物在馬路上，駕駛者經過時經常被「菜蘿」和「發泡膠箱」阻礙，道路本來的上落客貨區亦被車長期佔用，地上更滿是積水，衞生情況欠佳，不少街坊稱已向相關部門投訴，但有沒有改善？大家有眼睇，奉勸駕駛人士如無必要都不要駛進這條路障處處的瑞和街為妙。<br />\n<br />\n本地豬農：叉燒飯藏針相信源於為豬隻打針時用到的針咀被弄斷<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1130385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1130385</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街掃違例泊車 揭運魚車司機停牌駕駛<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1186592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1186592</a><br />\n<br />\n港府滅鼠落後 瑞和街市鼠患嚴重<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bLDCvS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bLDCvS</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街水果店雪櫃短路起火 逾百居民疏散<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1150423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1150423</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街發泡膠山圍城 空談回收政府袖手 <br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1091557\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1091557</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街後巷雜物遭縱火 警追緝縱火狂徒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cpqqsS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cpqqsS</a><br />\n<br />\n​「新界仔優質果菜」觀塘瑞和街分店持續播放叫賣錄音造成噪音煩擾被定罪<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/866940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/866940</a><br />\n<br />\n[全港最平] 瑞和街 橙售價為12元3個、菜心每斤9元，而生菜為5元一斤<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/912860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/912860</a>"},{"pid":"305ef16ba4fb4df03e85fd630dbee44488fba1c9","tid":1697001,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/13730840_539817879558146_5615744774723395600_o.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQn2YSKJG3nTrLNHc3IXPg_a9F_Xn4tkcNDCXyHYegOMrtB5sy03OOuAKN0fmdgUBUo&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=6d2bc54b69fcdb1ff6dcf6b1d54efb06&amp;oe=5E1AE52E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F13730840_539817879558146_5615744774723395600_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQn2YSKJG3nTrLNHc3IXPg_a9F_Xn4tkcNDCXyHYegOMrtB5sy03OOuAKN0fmdgUBUo%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D6d2bc54b69fcdb1ff6dcf6b1d54efb06%26oe%3D5E1AE52E&h=445e0caf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d30e86055ef0c4eb8db2fe7dcd0cf916859b837","tid":1697001,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"305ef16ba4fb4df03e85fd630dbee44488fba1c9","tid":1697001,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/13730840_539817879558146_5615744774723395600_o.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQn2YSKJG3nTrLNHc3IXPg_a9F_Xn4tkcNDCXyHYegOMrtB5sy03OOuAKN0fmdgUBUo&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=6d2bc54b69fcdb1ff6dcf6b1d54efb06&amp;oe=5E1AE52E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F13730840_539817879558146_5615744774723395600_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQn2YSKJG3nTrLNHc3IXPg_a9F_Xn4tkcNDCXyHYegOMrtB5sy03OOuAKN0fmdgUBUo%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D6d2bc54b69fcdb1ff6dcf6b1d54efb06%26oe%3D5E1AE52E&h=445e0caf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T14:27:32.000Z","msg":"興聯&gt;原味雞&gt;郭時興&gt;佳聯&gt;佳聯元朗&gt;王威信&gt;721<br />\n<br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e473b8a7b1462b1df9424da22b4be4ff8e725b","tid":1697001,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:20:47.000Z","msg":"核彈 冇人理"},{"pid":"2f2dce7c95dc236afec63b239262d4611d2c3e67","tid":1697001,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:35:00.000Z","msg":"NX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab3f1b3bbae897560d318ccd5812c42d6266a74","tid":1697001,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:37:44.000Z","msg":"世清屎都食"},{"pid":"5db9e654a253a885c1e2881fd86b1283acdfc76c","tid":1697001,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f2dce7c95dc236afec63b239262d4611d2c3e67","tid":1697001,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi