E}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20190906/photo/bkn-20190906190017129-0906_00982_001_01p.jpg?20190906190400\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20190906%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190906190017129-0906_00982_001_01p.jpg%3F20190906190400&h=7bd3472a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車然係咁：障礙處處的瑞和街<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560631</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條街對於觀塘區街坊而言無人不識，因為長期被兩旁商舖放滿雜物在馬路上，駕駛者經過時經常被「菜蘿」和「發泡膠箱」阻礙，道路本來的上落客貨區亦被車長期佔用，地上更滿是積水，衞生情況欠佳，不少街坊稱已向相關部門投訴，但有沒有改善？大家有眼睇，奉勸駕駛人士如無必要都不要駛進這條路障處處的瑞和街為妙。<br />\n<br />\n本地豬農：叉燒飯藏針相信源於為豬隻打針時用到的針咀被弄斷<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1130385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1130385</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街掃違例泊車 揭運魚車司機停牌駕駛<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1186592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1186592</a><br />\n<br />\n港府滅鼠落後 瑞和街市鼠患嚴重<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bLDCvS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bLDCvS</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街水果店雪櫃短路起火 逾百居民疏散<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1150423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1150423</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街發泡膠山圍城 空談回收政府袖手 <br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1091557\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1091557</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街後巷雜物遭縱火 警追緝縱火狂徒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cpqqsS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cpqqsS</a><br />\n<br />\n​「新界仔優質果菜」觀塘瑞和街分店持續播放叫賣錄音造成噪音煩擾被定罪<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/866940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/866940</a><br />\n<br />\n[全港最平] 瑞和街 橙售價為12元3個、菜心每斤9元，而生菜為5元一斤<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/912860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/912860</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"呢個所謂&quot;長期&quot;係講緊四五十年來都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0573a75ab4ae8cdcee98a8d211c4ce1f8542d2","tid":1697001,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:28:57.000Z","msg":"垃圾街黎 又臭又多雞"},{"pid":"ebe9104232e976729d98e3b12c90666ab52bb352","tid":1697001,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c0573a75ab4ae8cdcee98a8d211c4ce1f8542d2","tid":1697001,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:28:57.000Z","msg":"垃圾街黎 又臭又多雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:54:37.000Z","msg":"是"},{"pid":"89aec6215c6ddde97c81662f1ec0a6ccaa87de01","tid":1697001,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f635983eeaffa4daa48876dc332345abb48c198","tid":1697001,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:38:58.000Z","msg":"藍到發黑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:56:53.000Z","msg":"大家一齊1823"},{"pid":"1e89daa15fc535184fb2944d4be57ce0aa00d95a","tid":1697001,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89aec6215c6ddde97c81662f1ec0a6ccaa87de01","tid":1697001,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f635983eeaffa4daa48876dc332345abb48c198","tid":1697001,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:38:58.000Z","msg":"藍到發黑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:56:53.000Z","msg":"大家一齊1823"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:48:49.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"9ecefeb5412a6b01251fbac3057c845a69443cb5","tid":1697001,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21ee44fe7b467cc3c614b8672c4beb75ce66db75","tid":1697001,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d3b9ef19ad59f4e04ff4abdcb1e8bcedb68e0bf","tid":1697001,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T07:01:05.000Z","msg":"興聯同曼聯有無咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\